summary: BRAND MANAGER Mes Mes. Mes (as eppropriste) is the brand's senior vice president. He is responsible for brand marketing, legal and legal affairs. The law department is in charge of brand licensing and marketing. It is a joint venture between the Swedish and Norwegian governments.
